          <note>Note the unusual shape of <foreign>t</foreign>, with a loop.</note>
        </p>
        <p n="B.5">
          <term>°apano</term>
          <note>Note unusually round shape of <foreign>pa</foreign>.</note>
        </p>
      </div>
